File::Locate::Iterator reads a "locate" database file, similar to
File::Locate, but done as an iterator rather than callbacks.

Optional support for Iterator or Iterator::Simple iterators is
included, or the module can just be used natively.

The File-Locate-Iterator home page is

    http://user42.tuxfamily.org/file-locate-iterator/index.html
